  return (
    <ul>
      {items.map(item => <li>{item.name}</li>)}
    </ul>
  );
};
```

## Component Checklist
- [ ] Proper TypeScript interfaces defined
- [ ] No `any` types used
- [ ] Proper prop validation
- [ ] Error boundaries implemented
- [ ] Proper key props for lists
- [ ] No inline styles
- [ ] Proper event handling
- [ ] Memoization used when appropriate